力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfpGCZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfpGCZC.jpg&h=67926741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n唔好意思，最後想宣傳下，因為離個target仲差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 呢件事完全唔係我地發起，只係之前去威瑪做展覧connect到當地activists，佢哋話返俾我地知有呢件事發生咗。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T01:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}